      <ownedComment xmi:id="ae5d82be-8498-4f64-b4ae-ad6b732943fd" body="The {xor} constraint is applied to a set of associations, specifying that&#xA;over that set, exactly one is manifest for each associated instance. Xor is&#xA;an exclusive or (not inclusive or) constraint." annotatedElement="12d7cfee-8a6c-49e2-b830-446274b15c35">
